APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

2007-1812. State v. Harris.

Hamilton App. No. C-060587. Discretionary appeal accepted on Proposition of Law No. I; cause held for the decision in 2007-0595 and 2007-0651, State v. Cabrales, Hamilton App. No. C-050682, 2007-*1423Ohio-857; and briefing schedule stayed.
